<div class="govuk-!-margin-bottom-8">
  <h2 id="international-candidates" class="govuk-heading-l">International candidates</h2>

  {% if course.fundingType == "apprenticeship" %}
    {% set apprenticeshipHtml %}{% include "./international-candidates/apprenticeship.md" %}{% endset %}
    {{ apprenticeshipHtml | trim | markdownToHtml | safe  }}
  {% endif %}

  <p class="govuk-body">You’ll {{ "also" if course.fundingType == "apprenticeship" }} need the {{ 'right to work' if course.has_salary else 'right to study' }} in the UK. You already have this if, for example, you:</p>

  <ul class="govuk-list govuk-list--bullet">
    <li>are an Irish citizen</li>
    <li>have settled or pre-settled status under the <a class="govuk-link" href="https://www.gov.uk/settled-status-eu-citizens-families">EU Settlement Scheme</a> (you may still be able to apply)</li>
    <li>have indefinite leave to remain in the UK</li>
  </ul>

  {% set sponsorVisasHtml %}
    {% if (not course.hasSalary) and course.canSponsorStudentVisa %}
      {% include "./international-candidates/student-visas.md" %}
    {% elif course.hasSalary and provider.canSponsorSkilledWorkerVisa %}
      {% include "./international-candidates/skilled-worker-visas.md" %}
    {% elif course.hasSalary %}
      {% include "./international-candidates/salary.md" %}
    {% else %}
      {% include "./international-candidates/sponsorship-not-available.md" %}
    {% endif %}
  {% endset %}

  {{ sponsorVisasHtml | trim | markdownToHtml | safe  }}

  {% if course.hasIrp %}
    <p class="govuk-body">You may be entitled to £10,000 from the UK government to help with the financial costs of moving to England.</p>
  {% endif %}

  <p class="govuk-body">Learn more about <a class="govuk-link" href="https://getintoteaching.education.gov.uk/non-uk-teachers/train-to-teach-in-england-as-an-international-student">training to teach in England as an international student</a>.</p>

  <h3 class="govuk-heading-m">International qualifications</h3>

  <p class="govuk-body">If your qualifications come from a non-UK institution, we may want to see a ‘statement of comparability’ from UK ENIC. This will show us how they compare to UK qualifications.</p>

  <p class="govuk-body">You can call <a href="https://getintoteaching.education.gov.uk" class="govuk-link">Get Into Teaching</a> on 0800 389 2500 for:</p>

  <ul class="govuk-list govuk-list--bullet">
    <li>guidance on the UK equivalents of your qualifications</li>
    <li>a free statement of comparability once you’ve submitted your application (if we ask you for this)</li>
  </ul>

</div>
